==Devil May Cry 4 Special Soundtrack== {{Infobox album| <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject_Albums --> Cover = | Name = Devil May Cry 4 Special Soundtrack | Type = [[Soundtrack Album]] | Artist = [[Capcom]] | Producer = [[Tetsuya Shibata]] | Released = December 19, 2007 | Genre = [[Computer and video game music|Video Game Soundtrack]] | Length = 54:59 | Label = [[Avex Trax]] | Reviews = [http://www.squareenixmusic.com Square Enix Music Online] ([http://www.squareenixmusic.com/reviews/don/devilmaycry4promo.shtml link])}}
Released on December 19, 2007 in Japan, it comes with a CD with selected tracks from the game as well as a DVD with promotional videos. Female vocals are handled by Aubrey Ashburn ("Out of Darkness (Prologue)") while male vocals are handled by Shawn "Shootie HG" McPherson of Hostile Groove ("Sworn Through Swords" and "Lock and Load (Blackened Angel mix)") and Jason "ShyBoy" Arnold of Hypnogaja ("The Time Has Come" and "Shall Never Surrender (End Roll)").
